Net Brand 3.5mm Medial Distal Tibia Safety
Lock Plate with Tab

These plates are indicated for Extra-articular,
Partial articular and Complete articular complex

or simple fractures of distal tibia. These
Plates can be anatomically contoured to match

with the Distal Medial Tibia. The tab is provided
to be fixed over and to protect the Pilon

Holes in the head allow only 3.5mm safety
locking screws, rest holes allow both 3.5mm

These plates are designed separately for both
right and left tibia and are available in

a variety of lengths. These plates are available
with number of holes varying from 4 to 14
and are available in stainless steel and titanium.
